des:
Wake up with Tony and the family. Enable these alarm tones from HBO Max to start your morning with classic clips from each season of the HBO Original The Sopranos, now available to stream on HBO Max.

You can set it right now by saying, “Alexa, wake me up with The Sopranos Alarm tone every day at 7 AM.”
